content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 451.189 - Net worth

State Regulations

The aggregate appearing on the accounting records of the
equities representing proprietary interests; the excess of the going concern's
value of assets over liabilities to outsiders; of a corporation, the total of
paid-in capital, retained earnings and appropriated surplus; of a sole
proprietorship, the proprietor's account; of a partnership, the sum of the
partners' accounts. Notes
